items.badge_description:
Hoppy International Beer Day!

Beer serves as the common thread that links us worldwide, possessing the ability to bring people together in a unique way.

Beer has played a significant role in shaping countless of our most cherished memories. And if there’s one thing we’ve learned along the way, beer is best when shared with others.

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 325 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 66!

At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 205 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 42! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

Rye isn't just for liquor anymore and many breweries are proving this with delicious rye-style variants. With a unique mix of flavors and bitterness, it'll keep you coming back for more. That's 5 different beers with style of Rye Beer, IPA - Rye, Roggenbier, or Rye Wine. Try 5 more for Level 2!
